markets.title: Will the **federal funds rate** be above 0.75% following the Fed's March meeting?
markets.rules_primary: If the target federal funds rate is greater than 0.75% following the Federal Reserve's March meeting, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary: This market will expire the first 2:05 PM ET following the release of a Federal Reserve statement for their March 16, 2022 meeting or one week following the last day of that meeting.
